<h1>China Food Scandals Hit New Highs</h1>

<p><b>Hong Kong, October 8, 2014</b> – AsiaInspection (AI), a leading quality control service provider that partners with brands, retailers and importers around the world to secure, manage and optimize their supply chain, today announces its 2014 Q4 Barometer, a quarterly synopsis on outsourced manufacturing and the quality control services industry.</p>

